Keyboard shortcuts:

	Global:
	g then d - All discussions
	g then f - Followed discussions
	g then F - Favourite discussions
	g then c - Categories
	g then m - Conversations (messages)
x	Shift+j/k or n/p - Next/previous page

	In discussion list:
x	j/k and n/p - Next/previous item
x	o/enter - Open discussion (Hold shift to open in new tab)
	m - Mark as read
	r - Refresh list
x	c - New discussion
	
	Viewing posts:
	j/k and n/p - Next/previous post
	q - Quote post
	c - Go to compose reply
	r - Load new posts
	u - Back to discussions
